data.description: Darling home located on a corner lot on a quiet street.  This 2 bedroom home could easily be made into 4 with the additional space in the unfinished portion of the basement.  Entertaining is easy with 2 large family rooms, one on the main level and another in the basement! The updated kitchen has newer cabinets plus granite countertops.  The home features newer flooring, newer paint and newer interior doors.  Additionally, all main floor windows have been updated.  The basement has tons of storage with built in selves. The unfinished half bath has ample room to make it a full with an addition of a bath/shower.  This home has been well cared for and loved.
